    <item>
      <title>跟随中国债券指数走势，印度资本流入将降温</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/india-inflows-set-to-cool-following-china-s-bond-index-playbook</link>
      <description><![CDATA[如果中国的经验可以作为借鉴的话，那么在印度债券被纳入全球主要债务指数之前，购买印度债券的狂热将会暂停。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/india-inflows-set-to-cool-following-china-s-bond-index-playbook</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 01:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美元兑日元会再次突破160吗？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-30/would-dollar-yen-top-160-again</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚国民银行全球外汇策略主管 Ray Attrill 讨论了日元、美元、欧元的前景、债券收益率和央行的政策。他在“彭博社：亚洲黎明”节目中发表了讲话。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
