    <item>
      <title>必和必拓放弃以 490 亿美元收购英美资源集团</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-30/bhp-abandons-49-billion-bid-for-anglo-american</link>
      <description><![CDATA[必和必拓集团已决定不向英美资源集团提出确定报价。该集团目前放弃了这笔原本可能成为十多年来最大矿业交易的交易。克拉拉·费雷拉·马克斯在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-30/bhp-abandons-49-billion-bid-for-anglo-american</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 00:43:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>米莱伊的全面放松管制计划通过了参议院的第一次审核</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/milei-s-sweeping-deregulation-plan-passes-first-senate-hurdle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿根廷总统哈维尔·米莱 (Javier Milei) 为放松阿根廷经济管制而提出的主要立法尝试，在反对派控制的参议院陷入数周僵局之后，距离决定性投票又近了一步。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/milei-s-sweeping-deregulation-plan-passes-first-senate-hurdle</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 00:28:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>龙光地产 80 亿美元重组计划取决于豪华大厦贷款</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/logan-s-8-billion-restructuring-hinges-on-luxury-tower-loan</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国开发商龙光集团有限公司 (Logan Group Co.) 价值 80 亿美元的海外重组计划即将进入关键阶段，该公司只有三个月的时间来偿还或再融资贷款，否则将面临失去对一个重要豪宅项目控制权的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/logan-s-8-billion-restructuring-hinges-on-luxury-tower-loan</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 00:25:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>油价企稳，因交易商关注 OPEC+ 会议和美国库存</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-30</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价在周三下跌后持稳，交易员关注美国库存数据和周末的 OPEC+ 会议，以更清晰地了解供需前景。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-may-30</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 23:32:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：亚洲股市跟随美国同行走低，收益率攀升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市和债市周四下跌，与美国股市的跌势如出一辙，此前美国国债销量再次疲软，加剧了人们对收益率上升影响的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 22:23:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南公用事业公司在创纪录的电力需求下寻求更多节能措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/vietnam-s-utility-seeks-more-power-savings-amid-record-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南国营公用事业公司表示，尽管预计今年不会出现电力短缺，但该公司呼吁家庭、办公室和工厂减少用电量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-29/vietnam-s-utility-seeks-more-power-savings-amid-record-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 May 2024 11:31:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
